1. *Sinko* je došao u kuću ranije nego što je planirao. (He arrived at home earlier than he had planned.)
2. Zbog *sinka* su svi bili veseli. (Everyone was happy because of the arrival.)
3. Ona je očekivala da će *sinko* nositi poklone. (She expected that the arrival would bring presents.)
4. *Sinko* je donelo mnogo radosti u ovu kuću. (The arrival brought lots of joy to this house.)
5. Svi su se radovali *sinku*. (Everyone was happy about the arrival.)